headline: Could Domino's Pizza Be a Millionaire-Maker Stock?
summary: The stock's returns since 2010 would have turned a $15,000 investment into a position worth more than $1 million today -- and management plans to double the store count.

headline: Domino's® and Netflix Partner to Bring Emergency Pizza to the Squid Game Universe
summary: Domino's Pizza Inc. (NYSE: DPZ) is joining forces with Netflix Inc. (NASDAQ: NFLX) to prove that an Emergency Pizza can save the day – even in the high-stakes realm of Squid Game. As the hit Netflix series approaches its season two debut on Dec. 26, Domino's is activating at Squid Game: The Experience to give away free Emergency Pizza for a year to players with the lowest scores – just in time for when they need it most.
